id: pm-kb5h
title: "Source-tree folder-density program: bounded directory fan-out via domain-noun subfolders (zero feature loss)"
description: "Inter-file half of the 2026-07-12 too-many/too-long directive (intra-file LOC half = pm-yh8r): regroup high-fan-out directories (src/cli/commands 72, tests/unit/commands 60, tests/integration 32, scripts 23, src/cli 19) into domain-noun subfolders per the disposition blueprint in the body, in 6 fenced tranches."
type: Chore
status: open
priority: 2
