estimated_minutes: 600
acceptance_criteria: Every tracked source directory holds ≤~20 direct files or carries a documented exemption in this body; all moves land as import-specifier-only refactors with full gates green per tranche and byte-identical CLI/MCP/contract surface; pm files links updated for moved paths on open items in the same tranche; vitest/eslint-suppressions/coverage/package.json/workflow/docs references updated within the moving tranche
